<template><div><p>基于内容的推荐（Content-Based Filtering）是推荐系统中的另一个重要分支，其核心理念是 <strong>&quot;知其然，知其所以然&quot;</strong>。通过分析物品的内容特征和用户的历史偏好，构建用户画像，推荐具有相似内容特征的物品。</p>
<h2 id="🧠-核心思想与工作原理" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#🧠-核心思想与工作原理"><span>🧠 核心思想与工作原理</span></a></h2>
<div class="hint-container tip">
<p class="hint-container-title">🎨 特征驱动的智能推荐</p>
<p>基于内容的推荐依赖于物品的内容特征，通过学习用户对这些特征的偏好来进行推荐。</p>
</div>
<h3 id="算法直觉" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#算法直觉"><span>算法直觉</span></a></h3>
<p>想象你在选择电影：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>类型偏好</strong>：你喜欢科幻、动作类型的电影</li>
<li><strong>导演偏爱</strong>：你钟情于克里斯托弗·诺兰的作品</li>
<li><strong>演员喜好</strong>：你偏爱汤姆·汉克斯主演的电影</li>
<li><strong>智能推荐</strong>：系统基于这些偏好特征，推荐具有相似特征的新电影</li>
</ul>
<Mermaid id="mermaid-39" code=""></Mermaid><h3 id="数学表示" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#数学表示"><span>数学表示</span></a></h3>
<p>设物品 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6595em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span></span></span></span> 的特征向量为 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>c</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>∈</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="double-struck">R</mi><mi>d</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">c_i \in \mathbb{R}^d</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6891em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">c</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8491em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbb">R</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8491em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">d</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，用户 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">u</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span></span></span></span> 的偏好向量为 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>w</mi><mi>u</mi></msub><mo>∈</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="double-struck">R</mi><mi>d</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">w_u \in \mathbb{R}^d</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6891em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02691em;">w</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0269em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">u</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8491em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbb">R</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8491em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">d</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><strong>预测评分公式</strong>：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mover accent="true"><mi>r</mi><mo>^</mo></mover><mrow><mi>u</mi><mi>i</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mi>w</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>T</mi></msubsup><msub><mi>c</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>d</mi></munderover><msub><mi>w</mi><mrow><mi>u</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo>⋅</mo><msub><mi>c</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\hat{r}_{ui} = w_u^T c_i = \sum_{k=1}^{d} w_{uk} \cdot c_{ik}
